{
  "name": "RPlog_A_New_Moon_Rises",
  "title": "A New Moon Rises",
  "summary": "Aboard the luxury cruise liner Angry Rancor in orbit of Gastus, a relaxed gathering of passengers -- including Luke Skywalker, Lando Calrissian, and assorted New Republic personnel -- is shattered when a fully operational Death Star and a fleet of Star Destroyers emerge from hyperspace under Emperor Valak's command. As TIE fighters give chase, the horrified passengers watch the battle station fire its planet-killing beam and obliterate Gastus, after which the Rancor makes an emergency jump to Caspar. In the ensuing panic, New Republic officers led by General Arands and Captain Bazil McKenzie scramble to alert the warship Deliverance and seal the ship, while Lando bluffs the bridge into quarantining the liner. The Sith Moff Morganna seizes a hostage, Sam'viel, and tries to flee to the hangar, but Luke confronts her in a lightsaber duel and overpowers her, dislocating her shoulder before subduing and sedating her. With the chaos finally contained, the New Republic team -- and their captive Morganna, carried by the Quarren Kelvis -- board the shuttle Tiamant and depart for the Deliverance, vowing to warn the galaxy of the new Death Star.",
